data.description: Conveniently located to nearby hospital, Route 33, 78 , 22 ,recreation, shopping, dining, schools is this nice home located in West Easton! High Dollar items done in 2021 are as follow ,new 50 yr roof with transferable warranty, new vinyl siding , new privacy fence , front door and winter screen door . Home has a finished heated attic that can be used as an office, storage, or game room. Off street parking pad in the back . An above ground pool also included .Very efficient gas heat for peace of mind. Very nice yard with ample space to entertain guests. LOW TAXES !  Hurry...  Owner eager to sale. Bring your offer today ! Make your appt today!    Inspection Report uploaded FYI . Very minor issues.  Thank you.
